🟣 Phase 7: The Continuous Translation Engine (The "Sweet Spot" UI)
The Goal: Build a real-time system using a "Sliding Window" architecture that constantly processes the live webcam feed, dynamically extracts words from continuous motion using your optimized LSTM, and renders stable, on-screen sentences using state-based "Neutral Reset" logic.
